snippet.textDisplay: There are many ways custom mold can get to the hands of others. Are you certain that the factory you deal with has the capability to make their own molds? Specially if it’s a still mold. A rubber mold is only good for a certain amount of PCs and then you have to repay for a new mold. Most factories will commission their local hardware factory to make the molds. Also did you trademark the design? You must do this because if not the factory reserve the rights to use it a sample for other customers after a certain amount of time.
